We do this kind of procedure all the time.

789
01:00:25,405 --> 01:00:27,351
[OLIVIA SCREAMING]

790
01:00:28,741 --> 01:00:29,845
[SOBBING]

791
01:00:33,279 --> 01:00:35,452
Help me!

792
01:00:36,182 --> 01:00:37,752
Help me!

793
01:00:38,518 --> 01:00:41,522
[SCREAMING]

794
01:00:56,317 --> 01:00:58,160
DOTTIE
This has never happened before.

795
01:00:58,319 --> 01:01:00,458
[DOTTIE & DETECTIVE
SPEAKING INDISTINCTLY]

796
01:01:02,891 --> 01:01:04,529
Sam.

797
01:01:05,593 --> 01:01:07,903
Stay with me tonight, please.

798
01:01:09,030 --> 01:01:10,873
Of course.

799
01:01:15,737 --> 01:01:17,808
Five different systems had to go wrong...

800
01:01:17,972 --> 01:01:21,852
...for that laser to fail us
so spectacularly. Five.

801
01:01:22,010 --> 01:01:23,751
What do you want from us?

802
01:01:23,912 --> 01:01:26,222
I want you to tell me
what you think is going on.

803
01:01:26,381 --> 01:01:29,089
Two deaths? Okay, all right.
That's a coincidence.

804
01:01:29,250 --> 01:01:32,163
Three? That's a pattern.

805
01:01:45,166 --> 01:01:46,645
Now...

806
01:01:47,368 --> 01:01:49,644
...I know you two didn't do this.

807
01:01:50,872 --> 01:01:52,146
All right?

808
01:01:53,541 --> 01:01:55,919
But I think you know something.

809
01:01:58,580 --> 01:01:59,752
What is it?

810
01:02:01,850 --> 01:02:04,296
We don't know anything.

811
01:02:04,919 --> 01:02:07,195
Take a guess.

812
01:02:13,027 --> 01:02:16,531
We think we weren't supposed to survive
on that bridge.

813
01:02:17,866 --> 01:02:18,901
What?

814
01:02:19,567 --> 01:02:23,879
