Right now, yeah.

818
01:02:32,881 --> 01:02:37,557
But if you came up
with any other explanations, let us know.

819
01:02:40,221 --> 01:02:42,326
Thank you.

820
01:02:48,563 --> 01:02:50,338
"Something"

821
