NATHAN [OVER PA]: Roy, would you come
to the control room, please?

843
01:04:44,779 --> 01:04:47,521
MAN: Uh-ch, Roy, that's the boss.
You in trouble, Roy.

844
01:05:04,065 --> 01:05:06,306
ROY: Okay, schoolboy,
what do you wanna talk to me about?

845
01:05:06,467 --> 01:05:09,277
NATHAN: What is with your timecard?
