860
01:05:55,183 --> 01:05:59,495
Not the plant, just us.
Just sales and administration.

861
01:05:59,654 --> 01:06:01,327
Can you believe it? Us?

862
01:06:01,489 --> 01:06:03,662
It's the factory guys
that usually get laid off.

863
01:06:03,825 --> 01:06:05,361
Not us, we're supposed to be safe.

864
01:06:05,526 --> 01:06:07,904
Yeah, Dennis, we get bigger problems.

865
01:06:08,763 --> 01:06:10,504
Olivia and Isaac are dead.

866
01:06:11,499 --> 01:06:12,603
Who's Isaac?

867
01:06:12,767 --> 01:06:15,839
Isaac Palmer, tech support.

868
01:06:16,904 --> 01:06:18,178
Wasn't he dead already?

869
01:06:18,339 --> 01:06:19,716
No, Dennis.

870
01:06:19,907 --> 01:06:25,220
Listen, it's going to happen to us too
if we don't do something about it.

871
01:06:25,847 --> 01:06:29,192
Yeah, I understand.
Listen, it's called survivor's guilt.

872
01:06:29,350 --> 01:06:33,457
No. No, guilt doesn't kill you.

873
01:06:33,621 --> 01:06:35,567
Obviously, you've never met my in-laws.

874
01:06:35,723 --> 01:06:37,532
I'm not fucking around here, Dennis.

875
01:06:37,992 --> 01:06:39,562
