877
01:06:42,530 --> 01:06:44,009
Nobody's safe.

878
01:06:44,165 --> 01:06:45,701
What are you talking about?

879
01:06:48,002 --> 01:06:50,710
We weren't supposed to survive
that bridge collapse.

880
01:06:50,872 --> 01:06:53,751
And so new it's kill or be killed.

881
01:06:54,342 --> 01:06:56,515
You get that, Dennis?

882
01:06:57,645 --> 01:06:58,680
Whatever.

883
01:06:58,846 --> 01:07:01,690
I warned you.
Do whatever you wanna do.

884
01:07:03,718 --> 01:07:04,822
[DOOR CLOSES]

885
01:07:05,520 --> 01:07:07,227
I will.

886
01:07:12,026 --> 01:07:14,336
Hey, Agent Black, it's Dennis. Um--

887
01:07:14,495 --> 01:07:18,409
