what the hell happened?

913
01:08:47,121 --> 01:08:48,156
Who is it, Sam?

914
01:08:48,322 --> 01:08:49,357
Who's what?

915
01:08:50,992 --> 01:08:53,802
[ALL GASPING]

916
01:08:54,662 --> 01:08:57,165
Dennis! It was Dennis.

917
01:08:57,632 --> 01:08:59,612
No shit.

918
01:09:00,635 --> 01:09:02,376
MAN:
Jesus.

919
01:09:05,640 --> 01:09:07,483
