922
01:09:14,649 --> 01:09:17,323
If Death is gonna came for me,
I don't think it matters where I am.

923
01:09:17,485 --> 01:09:19,226
You have to do something.

924
01:09:19,387 --> 01:09:22,129
-What, kill someone so I can live?
-No, of course not.

925
01:09:22,890 --> 01:09:25,029
We'll just have to
figure something else out.

926
01:09:25,193 --> 01:09:27,264
I have figured it out.

927
01:09:27,728 --> 01:09:30,709
Something saved me on that bridge.

928
01:09:30,865 --> 01:09:32,708
Maybe it doesn't want me to die.

929
01:09:35,036 --> 01:09:36,515
Maybe.

930
01:09:36,671 --> 01:09:39,550
We can't live our lives in fear, Moll.

931
01:09:41,909 --> 01:09:46,221
So if it happens tomorrow,
or 50 years from now, whatever.

932
01:09:46,380 --> 01:09:48,587
As long as we're together...

933
01:09:49,850 --> 01:09:51,056
...I'll be okay.

934
01:09:53,754 --> 01:09:56,598
Right? Why don't you came by
after my shift...

935
01:09:56,757 --> 01:09:58,862
