966
01:12:33,914 --> 01:12:36,417
If the offer still stands...

967
01:12:36,584 --> 01:12:37,927
...I'd like to take it.

968
01:12:39,587 --> 01:12:41,089
It's yours.

969
01:12:45,693 --> 01:12:48,833
[WOMAN SPEAKING INDISTINCTLY
OVER RADIO]

970
01:12:55,803 --> 01:12:57,282
SAM:
Okay, no more suspense.

971
01:12:57,438 --> 01:12:58,917
[MOLLY CHUCKLES]

972
01:12:59,073 --> 01:13:01,110
