980
01:13:20,694 --> 01:13:24,608
What? Sam, that's amazing.

981
01:13:27,968 --> 01:13:29,777
I'm so proud of you.

982
01:13:46,954 --> 01:13:49,696
-Peter.
-Hey.

983
01:13:51,492 --> 01:13:54,530
You okay, man?
You lack a little, uh, upset.

984
01:13:54,695 --> 01:13:58,643
Yeah. Yeah, yeah, yeah.
Just a rough couple days.

985
01:13:59,333 --> 01:14:02,007
Yeah. Yeah, for everyone.

986
01:14:02,970 --> 01:14:04,847
For some more than others.

987
01:14:05,639 --> 01:14:07,084
Do you mind if I came in?

988
01:14:07,241 --> 01:14:09,585
Oh, yeah, of course. Yeah, came in.

989
01:14:15,249 --> 01:14:16,728
Here, have a seat.

990
01:14:17,585 --> 01:14:19,155
Thanks.

991
01:14:23,324 --> 01:14:24,598
Hey, Peter.

992
01:14:25,726 --> 01:14:27,535
Hi, Molly.

993
01:14:42,343 --> 01:14:46,155
Peter, can I get you anything to eat?
I can make you up some pasta.

994
01:14:46,747 --> 01:14:50,285
Uh, no. No, no, no. I'm good.
Uh, thank you.

995
01:14:51,785 --> 01:14:53,628
Uh, I'm sorry. I just thought--

996
01:14:53,787 --> 01:14:56,358
It's good that you're here.
You shouldn't be alone right now.

997
01:14:56,991 --> 01:14:59,437
Yeah, you know,
I'm surprised I'm here at all.

998
01:15:00,861 --> 01:15:02,306
Uh ....

999
01:15:02,463 --> 01:15:04,272
Still alive, I mean.

1000
01:15:04,431 --> 01:15:05,774
I'm next to go, right?

1001
01:15:07,101 --> 01:15:08,774
It's me and then you, isn't it?

1002
01:15:11,572 --> 01:15:16,419
Anyways, uh, I was up all last night,
you know...

1003
01:15:16,577 --> 01:15:19,751
...thinking about if I could really do it.

1004
01:15:20,381 --> 01:15:24,193
-Do what?
-Take someone else's life.

1005
01:15:24,351 --> 01:15:29,596
If I could actually kill some stranger,
replace their life with my own.

1006
01:15:30,558 --> 01:15:32,469
And I thought about it.

1007
01:15:33,260 --> 01:15:35,262
And I convinced myself that...

1008
01:15:36,630 --> 01:15:38,166
